<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürgelegt
                            <add>Heinrich</add> Hirszvogel und Jacob <expan>Neydu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        wie <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dyener <add>in bey einem irem
                            poten</add>
<expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Cöln und Bunn etliche kleynod aufgehalten
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und niht
                            <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan>. Also tun wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> czu wissen, daz dy
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<add><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan></add> Hirszvogel und Jacob
                                <expan>Neydu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> sind. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> mit den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>, die das
                        getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, schicken und
                            <expan>bestalle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<add><expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dinst</add>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ire kleynod genczlich
                                <expan>widerwerde<ex>n</ex></expan> als etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>Sc<ex>ri</ex>pt<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
